                          ; XPK-Packer. If this fails, the file keeps
                          ; unpacked.


  File Format Information
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  As "Aminet:util/dtype/akSVG43x.lha" there's a separate package available,
  which consists of a "SVG.datatype" for applications not using
  SuperView-Library, @{"the description of the file format" LINK SVG_Specs } and
  a conversion tool "AnyToSVG" (using Datatypes upto 24 Bit).


  History
  ~~~~~~~
