@NODE SVOBJECT_IMG "IMG.svobject"

  © 1994-2001 by Andreas R. Kleinert.
  FREEWARE. All rights reserved. Only to be distributed with SuperView-Library.

  Version      : 4.9
  Release Date : 30.10.1998

  Description
  ~~~~~~~~~~~
  IMG.svobject is an external library module for superview.library,
  which needs any SVDriver with Bitplane-Support.

  It supports reading of IMG (GEM/Metafile) files.
  In detail these are :

  Reading :

   - IMG (16 byte header) grayscaled (1..8 bits = 2..256 scales)
   - IMG (18 byte header) grayscaled (1..8 bits = 2..256 scales)

  History
  ~~~~~~~
  V4.9 (30.10.2000) :

   - minor optimizations
   - improved memory management

  V4.8 (04.10.1998) :

