@NODE SVOPERATOR_ScaleDDA "ScaleDDA"

  © 1999 by Andreas R. Kleinert.
  FREEWARE. All rights reserved. Only to be distributed with SuperView-Library.

  Version      : 3.1
  Release Date : 24.09.1999

  Description
  ~~~~~~~~~~~
  ScaleDDA.svoperator is an external SV_GfxBuffer modification module
  for superview.library.

  ScaleDDA.svoperator scales any (upto) 256 Color or 24 bit graphics
  by a given zoom factor, thus increasing its size by a factor larger
